    "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nWith https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/issues/5633 , https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/issues/5634 , https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/issues/5635 , https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/issues/5636 implemented in  [PR-5998](https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/pull/5998) we need to evaluate the implementation decisions to achieve the following:\r\n\r\n- Study the impact of the supporting the JCudf in the plugin\r\n  - time performance\r\n  - memory efficiency\r\n- Evaluate the impact of various strategies on the transition performance such as:\r\n  - estimate string size\r\n  - initial dataBuffer size used for batch (see initial discussion: https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/pull/5998#issuecomment-1191908960)\r\n  - policy on using GPU optimized kernel..etc\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nIn addition to evaluate benchmarks like NDS, we need to add a microbenchmarking environment to help evaluating the performance of JCudf transitions along with the following features:\r\n\r\n- In an experimental branch we need some few configurations to turn on/off some of the key decisions:\r\n  - configs to turn-on/off support of JCudf transitions for certain types in the plugin.\r\n  - configs to turn-on/off packed schemas: study impact of pact vs unpacked on memory and performance\r\n  - configs to decide on initial minimum dataBuffer size used for batch-row iteration\r\n  - configs to change variable-width column sizes\r\n  - configs to change policy whether to use optimized GPU kernel.\r\n- Be able to run against different Spark releases\r\n- The workload needs to cover the following:\r\n  - explore if more optimization to be done for NULL values \r\n  - access patterns of columns: for example impact of packing schema on locality of accessing columns.\r\n  - schemas with large number of variable-width columns\r\n  - schemas with small number of variable-width columns\r\n  - schemas with large/small sizes of variable-width columns\r\n\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n\r\n- This is a subtask of Epic issue https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/issues/507\r\n- PR adding support to String columns [PR-5998](https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/pull/5998)\r\n- Depends on\r\n  - https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/issues/5633 ,\r\n  - https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/issues/5634 ,\r\n  - https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/issues/5635 , \r\n  - https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/issues/5636\r\n",
